{"tid":1031523,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"北京同仁堂被撤質量獎","createTime":"2019-02-21T16:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T16:45:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"10b0071aabe3c8942ad6e7ce13f8c50af7c23536","tid":1031523,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190221/20617418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190221%2F20617418&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHDyKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=eeabca5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190221%2F20617418&h=bb362db0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190221/20617418</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北京同仁堂被撤質量獎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190221/large/bj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190221%2Flarge%2Fbj.jpg&h=8c9dffa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在香港設有多間分店的北京同仁堂（圖）去年被內地傳媒揭發，其蜂蜜生產商回收大量過期蜂蜜，懷疑回收再用。國家市場監管總局周一宣佈，撤銷北京同仁堂的中國質量獎稱號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用過期蜂蜜<br />\n<br />\n內地電視台去年報道，同仁堂蜂業委託的生產商，將過期或臨近過期的蜂蜜，倒進大桶回收並送入原料庫。公司其後承認監管不力，並封存產品。早前北京、山東等地的監管部門已公佈處罰，包括問責負責人、罰款1,408.8萬元人民幣（約1,646萬港元）及吊銷牌照。根據法例，獲獎組織和個人兩年內發生重大品質和安全事故或違法違紀行為，需要撤銷獎勵並公開通報。同仁堂產品近年屢被查出質量問題，包括2018年63個批次甘草片不合格、2016年阿膠中驗出豬和牛的DNA等，內地傳媒形容為「質量黑榜」常客。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊網<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n「象牙女王」非洲走私囚15年罰款1億"},{"pid":"e261e542094d16fac90ea5fa5c10604e933ed058","tid":1031523,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T16:45:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}